{"data":{"post":{"id":"a4e165b3-44ca-59b9-a5dd-b46301936d69","html":"<h1>Get Ubuntu run on Mac by docker</h1>\n<p>Due to unknown reasons, VirtualBox happens to crash on latest macOS Catalina. Here is an alternate way to run ubuntu on macOS.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You will be able to have a folder called “ubuntu” on your desktop which linked to /src/ in ubuntu.</li>\n<li>You will be able to start ubuntu in about 1 second.</li>\n<li>Docker container takes less resources on your computer than vm.</li>\n<li>BUT no graphic user interface.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>1. Download Docker (1.5 min)</h2>\n<p>Copy and paste the following link to the address bar of your preferred bowser would start the download of <a href=\"https://download.docker.com/mac/stable/Docker.dmg\">Docker-Desktop for Mac</a>.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/download-4e39cd86a2a87a9171958dd33549cc4f-03fd9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 74.24381301558202%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"download\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/download-4e39cd86a2a87a9171958dd33549cc4f-48538.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/download-4e39cd86a2a87a9171958dd33549cc4f-bed0f.png 200w,\n/static/download-4e39cd86a2a87a9171958dd33549cc4f-5fd34.png 400w,\n/static/download-4e39cd86a2a87a9171958dd33549cc4f-48538.png 800w,\n/static/download-4e39cd86a2a87a9171958dd33549cc4f-b70ec.png 1200w,\n/static/download-4e39cd86a2a87a9171958dd33549cc4f-d134a.png 1600w,\n/static/download-4e39cd86a2a87a9171958dd33549cc4f-03fd9.png 2182w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<!-- <img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006y8mN6gy1g7tqmoitb7j314f0u0naw.jpg\" style=\"width:80vw;margin:auto\"> -->\n<h2>2. Install Docker (1 min)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Drag and drop Docker into Application folder. And wait for the process to complete.\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/drag and drop-aef7c26b40b8f2408e37c5638c58be6e-85fa1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32692307692307%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"drag and drop\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/drag and drop-aef7c26b40b8f2408e37c5638c58be6e-48538.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/drag and drop-aef7c26b40b8f2408e37c5638c58be6e-bed0f.png 200w,\n/static/drag and drop-aef7c26b40b8f2408e37c5638c58be6e-5fd34.png 400w,\n/static/drag and drop-aef7c26b40b8f2408e37c5638c58be6e-48538.png 800w,\n/static/drag and drop-aef7c26b40b8f2408e37c5638c58be6e-b70ec.png 1200w,\n/static/drag and drop-aef7c26b40b8f2408e37c5638c58be6e-d134a.png 1600w,\n/static/drag and drop-aef7c26b40b8f2408e37c5638c58be6e-85fa1.png 1664w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n<img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006y8mN6gy1g7tqn5srfzj31a80p4qe1.jpg\" style=\"width:80vw;\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>When completed, you should be able to see Docker in your launchpad.\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/launchpad-16852c4dae00a9994528bc6842b4d2ff-6200b.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"launchpad\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/launchpad-16852c4dae00a9994528bc6842b4d2ff-48538.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/launchpad-16852c4dae00a9994528bc6842b4d2ff-bed0f.png 200w,\n/static/launchpad-16852c4dae00a9994528bc6842b4d2ff-5fd34.png 400w,\n/static/launchpad-16852c4dae00a9994528bc6842b4d2ff-48538.png 800w,\n/static/launchpad-16852c4dae00a9994528bc6842b4d2ff-b70ec.png 1200w,\n/static/launchpad-16852c4dae00a9994528bc6842b4d2ff-d134a.png 1600w,\n/static/launchpad-16852c4dae00a9994528bc6842b4d2ff-f6ead.png 2400w,\n/static/launchpad-16852c4dae00a9994528bc6842b4d2ff-6200b.png 2880w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n<img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006y8mN6gy1g7tqnirhwoj31c00u0npd.jpg\" style=\"width:80vw;\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>3. Start Docker (0.5 min)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Click Docker in the launchpad to start it. You should then be able to see Docker icon in the status bar.\n<img src=\"./status%20bar\">\n<img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006y8mN6gy1g7tqnsmx7aj312s0u0jts.jpg\" style=\"width:80vw;\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Sign up and login into a docker account is not necessary. Just wait util it shows “Docker Desktop is running”.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006y8mN6gy1g7tqoduzn9j30em0jw17n.jpg\" style=\"width:80vw;\">\n<h2>Get Ubuntu run (1 min)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Open Spotlight Search  <code class=\"language-text\">⌘ + SPACE</code>  and type “terminal” in the pop-up window.</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006y8mN6gy1g7tqoumifxj317u0u0al9.jpg\" style=\"width:80vw;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Open Terminal.</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006y8mN6gy1g7tqpdjf8bj316f0u0dms.jpg\" style=\"width:80vw;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Copy and paste the following code. Press Enter to run.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> /Users/<span class=\"token variable\">$USER</span>/Desktop/ubuntu<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndocker run \\\n  —name ubuntu \\\n  -e HOST_IP<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">ifconfig</span> en0 <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">awk</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/ *inet /{print <span class=\"token variable\">$2</span>}'</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span> \\\n  -v /Users/<span class=\"token variable\">$USER</span>/Desktop/ubuntu:/src \\\n  -t -I \\\n  ubuntu /bin/bash</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>If you see something like this, Ubuntu is already up and running.\n<img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006y8mN6gy1g7tqpo49p5j316f0u0n5d.jpg\" style=\"width:80vw;\"></li>\n<li>You are now in the ubuntu. Check by run  <code class=\"language-text\">cat /etc/lsb-release</code>\n<img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006y8mN6gy1g7tqpusektj316f0u0wpp.jpg\" style=\"width:80vw;\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Install dependency and tools (0.5 min)</h2>\n<p>Continue in the previous window, run the following code one by one.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> update</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> upgrade</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token function\">nano</span> g++</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Congratulations</h2>\n<p>Next time when you want to use ubuntu, just open terminal and run</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker start ubuntu<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> docker <span class=\"token function\">exec</span> -it ubuntu /bin/bash</code></pre></div>\n<p>Make sure Docker is running before run the code.</p>\n<p>P.S. You can create a new profile in terminal that run this code at start to save time.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/Mac-Docker-ubuntu/","prefix":"2019-10-11"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Run Ubuntu on Mac via Docker","author":"yujie wang","category":"Environment","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/photo-1490474418585-ba9bad8fd0ea-69657d5d9f9e2a2aa0aa1c3e268ce4a1-ada8c.jpg"}}}}},"authornote":{"id":"7dca60f9-6174-5308-b1d6-29aa40a88701","html":"<p><strong>Yujie</strong> Amateur web developer, currently study Electronic and Information Engineering in Imperial College London.</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Mac-Docker-ubuntu/","prev":{"id":"09542bb0-8fef-54ce-afd8-f8a6109e51b4","fields":{"slug":"/draft-post/","prefix":"","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"This is a draft post","category":"sayings"}},"source":"posts"}}